272
00:14:40,560 --> 00:14:43,440
I don't think this is a good place
for a 10-year-old boy.

273
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:47,210
Here's $5.
Buy yourself a suit and get busy.

274
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:48,880
I'll buy a suit...

275
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,250
...of drugs!

276
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,930
