280
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:09,510
That couch looks really pricey.

281
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:12,350
Well, you need an expensive couch
to watch an expensive TV.

282
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:14,490
Of course,
because you wouldn't want to...

283
