I paid for your splendor, you...

284
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,540
[GRUNTING]

285
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,120
[SIGHS]

286
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,420
And for every syringe I find,
I get a dollar.

287
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,850
