313
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,070
The next day,
they're grinding their way to college.

314
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:47,750
Yeah, I make up words too.

315
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,220
I was wondering
if you could pretend to lose to me...

316
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:53,350
...in a skateboarding contest
so I can be a hero to my boy again.

317
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:56,520
I'll lose millions in endorsements,
but okay.

318
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,250
This board represents the ultimate
in poser technology.

319
00:17:00,760 --> 00:17:03,040
- It gives the illusion they have talent.
- Groovy.

320
00:17:03,560 --> 00:17:05,450
Lock your feet in,
the board does all the work.

321
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:06,900
All the work?

322
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,080
[SIGHS]

323
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:11,070
Fine. I'll lift you onto the board too.

324
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:13,190
[GRUNTING]

325
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:16,400
