334
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,580
Back up again.
That's how the game is played.

335
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:40,270
I can't count how many times...

336
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:42,780
...your father's done something crazy
like this.

337
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:45,880
LISA:
It's 300, Mom.

338
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:47,960
I could've sworn it was 302.

339
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:49,520
Shh.

340
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,280
