341
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:59,350
Now to win back my son
in comfort and style.

342
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:07,330
[HUMMING]

343
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:14,490
You know, I could save money
by buying separate nuts...

344
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:16,310
...and mixing them at home.

345
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,690
Man, I wanted him to look good,
but not to show me up.

346
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,570
It's time to take out the thrash.

347
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,900
[BOTH GRUNTING]

348
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,220
TONY:
Take that.

349
00:18:39,560 --> 00:18:41,380
[BOTH HUMMING]

350
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,430
[BOTH GRUNTING]

351
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:46,800
