353
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:54,110
Come back to me, boy.

354
00:18:54,480 --> 00:18:55,640
Dad, you don't understand.

355
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:59,650
This was never about being cool,
it was about you not caring how I felt.

356
00:19:00,360 --> 00:19:02,960
