364
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:29,600
Mr. Simpson, I like the way
you handled yourself on that board.

365
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,640
Would you like to do a commercial?

366
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:35,160
Anything. As long as I can give
the money to my son.

367
00:19:35,800 --> 00:19:39,770
